    <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Principle/seven_non-binding_ethical_principles_for_AI>;
  euai:relation <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Principle/seven_non-binding_ethical_principles_for_AI>;
  euai:includedIn <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Principle/seven_non-binding_ethical_principles_for_AI> .

<https://euaiact.eu/resource/Principle/technical_robustness_and_safety> euai:structuralRelation
    <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Principle/seven_non-binding_ethical_principles_for_AI>;
